'''加菲爾德'''（{{lang|en|'''Garfield'''}}）為[[美國|美國]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[波尼縣_(堪薩斯州)|波尼縣]]的一座城市。根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，此城市人口有190人<ref name="Census2010">{{cite web |title=2010 City Population and Housing Occupancy Status |url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table |publisher=U.S. Census Bureau |accessdate=2011-09-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721034521/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table |archivedate=2011-07-21 }}</ref>。

==歷史==
加菲爾德以[[美国总统|美國第20任總統]][[詹姆斯·艾布拉姆·加菲尔德|詹姆斯·艾布拉姆·加菲尔德]]為名<ref>{{cite book | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9V1IAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA134#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=The Origin of Certain Place Names in the United States | publisher=Govt. Print. Off. | author=Gannett, Henry | year=1905 | pages=134 | access-date=2016-09-30 | archive-date=2016-05-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509213938/https://books.google.com/books?id=9V1IAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA134#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

此城市首座郵政局於1873年開設<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:PN |title=Kansas Post Offices, 1828-1961 |publisher=Kansas Historical Society |accessdate=2014-06-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009123040/http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county%3APN |archivedate=2013-10-09 }}</ref>。

==地理==
加菲爾德坐落在北緯38度4分35秒、西經99度14分42秒（亦可表示成38.076310, -99.244994）<ref name="GR1">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2011-04-23|date=2011-02-12|title=US Gazetteer files: 2010, 2000, and 1990|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060720110047/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|archive-date=2006-07-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。根據[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的資料，此城市總面積為{{convert|0.54|sqmi|sqkm|2}}，全境皆為陸地<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2012-07-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

